==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*κακία / kakia / kak-ee'-ah
*From [[κακος|G2556]]; badness, that is, (subjectively) depravity, or (actively) malignity, or (passively) trouble: 

===Noun===
'''κακία'''

#[[evil]], [[malice]] (-iousness), [[naughtiness]], [[wickedness]].

